Sentencas: We prepared gadolinia-doped ceria (GDC) barrier layers by sputtering and annealing at various temperatures.
Titulo: Gadolinia-doped ceria barrier layer produced by sputtering and annealing for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: We then investigated the effects of the GDC barrier layers on the performance of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Gadolinia-doped ceria barrier layer produced by sputtering and annealing for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Sputtering at 200 degrees C readily produced a uniform, thin layer of cubic GDC.
Titulo: Gadolinia-doped ceria barrier layer produced by sputtering and annealing for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Sputtering and annealing at 900-1100 degrees C formed uniform, thin, dense films, which effectively prevented the reaction between the yttria-stabilized zirconia electrolyte and the Ba0.5Sr0.5Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta cathode.
Titulo: Gadolinia-doped ceria barrier layer produced by sputtering and annealing for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The single cells assembled with the thin, dense GDC barrier layers sputtered at 200 C and annealed at 900-1000 degrees C exhibited excellent electrochemical performance.
Titulo: Gadolinia-doped ceria barrier layer produced by sputtering and annealing for anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells
